sentences.english: Yongbyon is approximately 60 miles [96 kilometers] north of the capital at Pyongyang.

sentences.english: At the cost balance point on the institutional margin, the allocation of power achieves Pareto Optimality.
sentences.chinese: 在制度边际成本持平处权力的配置达到帕累托最优。

sentences.english: He doesn't get along with anybody in the office.
sentences.chinese: 他和办公室任何人都处不来。

sentences.english: Replaces the item at the specified index with a new object.
sentences.chinese: 使用指定项替换指定索引处的项。

sentences.english: They knock each other off balance just a little bit.
sentences.chinese: 她说，“他们只是一点点敲击彼此的不平衡之处。”

sentences.english: A new graveyard has been added near the east coast of the Hinterlands at the Overlook Cliffs.

sentences.english: Wrap from the lower part of outdoor unit to the position where the duct bundle passes through the wall.

sentences.english: She brought up the water, stopping at each landing to get her breath.
sentences.chinese: 她提水上楼，在每个楼梯平台处停下来喘口气。

sentences.english: That which festers must eventually explode.
sentences.chinese: 溃烂之处最终必须爆发。

sentences.english: During the teaching force of the subtleties will be passed to students, respected by the disciples.
sentences.chinese: 教学期间将武之奥妙之处传给师生，受到弟子尊敬。

sentences.chinese: 拿着水枪玩耍，喷得到处都是水，让妈妈非常生气。

sentences.english: Result 81 occult fractures were found in 42 cases.
sentences.chinese: 结果42例患者共81处隐匿性骨折。

sentences.english: A group of armed guards have arrived and are waiting outside the gate.
sentences.chinese: 一队武装警卫抵达并守卫在牢房区大门处。

sentences.english: Butterfly shapes accentuate the sweetness of heart-shaped faces.
sentences.chinese: 蝶形的太阳镜会凸显处心形脸的甜美。

sentences.english: You can then return to Grizelda and report your success.
sentences.chinese: 你返回格丽泽达处报告任务成功完成。
